"```sql\nSELECT d.forename, d.surname, d.url\nFROM results r\nJOIN races ra ON r.raceId = ra.raceId\nJOIN drivers d ON r.driverId = d.driverId\nWHERE ra.year = 2008\n  AND ra.name = 'Australian Grand Prix'\n  AND r.time LIKE '%:%:%.%';\n```\nThis SQL query retrieves the forename, surname, and URL of the driver who was the champion of the 2008 Australian Grand Prix. The condition `r.time LIKE '%:%:%.%'` is used to identify the champion, as only the champion's finished time is represented in the format 'HH:MM:SS.mmm'."